headline: Capture the Magic of Autumn with Chocolove's Irresistibly Tasty Pumpkin-Shaped Bites
summary: Chocolove, the Boulder, Colo.-based leader in chocolate quality, flavor innovation and sustainability for 30 years, is announcing the return of its beloved Pumpkin-Shaped Fall Bites, this time in new elegant, stand-up bags. The individually wrapped seasonal bites in Dark Chocolate Peanut Butter and Milk Chocolate Pumpkin Spice are thoughtfully crafted for fall festivities and enjoying on cozy nights at home.

headline: CVS agrees to pay Massachusetts $12M to settle Medicaid overbilling claims
summary: The retail pharmacy giant has also agreed to annually review its practices to ensure the state’s Medicaid program is getting the lowest possible prices for prescription drugs.
